0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"781f5f47e97ab68843d22fbd12fc87c5ac235819","tid":2313661,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e0af7fa00ba6b664fce01b9c793191dec338be06","tid":2313661,"uid":363335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"59684786a92ed4ccc9ef7b4c574639d22acf1ec6","tid":2313661,"uid":152048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:59:44.000Z","msg":"下年會喺英國讀完master，e展仔嚟嘅<br />\n想請問下我係咪要喺英國做多六年嘢，夠十年先得？上綱睇咗好多文，個個都唔同講法有啲亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求巴打解解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"你上到 Tier 2 visa 嘅話，五年就得。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"我degree其實都喺英國讀唔知有冇得加埋入去呢<br />\n同埋我見到啲網站話做五年得permenant citizen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T15:23:32.000Z","msg":"冇。非歐盟人士入籍英國分兩類：<br />\n<br />\nSettlement visa: Tier 1, Tier 2 general, dependent of UK citizen. BNO visa 出年生效之後會加入呢類。 住滿五年就可以攞永久居留權，之後再住一年就可以申請入籍。<br />\n<br />\nLong residence: 任何合法居留（包括以上同埋 Tier 4, Tier 5）連續超過十年，就可以攞永久居留權，之後亦係住多一年可以入籍。<br />\n<br />\n所以你喺英國讀過書嘅話，要睇你連續讀咗幾多年。未夠五年嘅話，攞到 Tier 2 (出年改名 professional immigrant) 排淨係計 Tier 2 五年嗰條隊最快。多過五年嘅話，排計晒所有 visa 總共十年嗰條隊最快。"}]}